{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "Did my Corrupted... get stopped by the guards... Why aren't they here...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "It won't be long... before the Punishing Virus is completely gone here..", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "...You're finally—h-here!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'W-why—i-is it you?!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "I can't fight a Construct like her... with the power from the Punishing Virus...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Roland the Ascendant, you better come with Nanami!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami's going to take down your frame and your M.I.N.D.!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hmm? You don't look... right.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: '(Chuckles) You do pick the right time to show up...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "I've no strength left to deal with you... however...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "If you want to catch me... you'll have to go through Nat's guards first...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami's afraid of no guards! So stay there and behave, alright? Do—not—move!", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Nanami immediately rushes toward the guards...'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Maybe if I turn off the power input from the Punishing Virus...', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Who could have thought that an Ascendant like me... would need to use the power of an ordinary frame...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: '(Looks up to find Nanami standing in front of him already) What... are you doing? The guards are behind you!', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Do you mean it?!', 4: '2'}
